drm/i915/gvt: Fix incorrect mask of mmio 0x22028 in gen8/9 mmio list

According to GFX PRM on 01.org, bit 31:16 of mmio 0x22028 should be masks.

Fixes: 178657139307 ("drm/i915/gvt: vGPU context switch")
